      "content": "The draft looks fine, but to be honest, I'm a bit worried about whether the new model can actually maintain that \"personal touch\" you're talking about. It's faster, sure, but it's also much more stripped down. I haven't seen how it handles the nuance of our high-net-worth requests yet. Can you write a section for the guide that specifically outlines the complex, multi-layered itinerary planning and personalized concierge nuances that are standard now, so if the new model misses them, the clients are at least prepared for a change in service depth?",
